milestones.description: Wessels's 71 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SA), surpassing Wessels's 50
Wessels has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (24) in an innings in ODIs for SA, going past Adrian Kuiper's 18
Wessels and Mandy Yachad's 94-run partnership is SA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 25 between Wessels and Jimmy Cook
Richardson and Clive Rice's 17-run partnership is SA's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 5 between Richard Snell and Clive Rice
Matthews and Clive Eksteen's 18-run partnership is SA's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Richardson and Tim Shaw
This is the highest match aggregate (408) involving teams South Africa & India in ODIs
Jimmy Cook has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for SA, going past Allan Donald
Wessels and Mandy Yachad's 94-run partnership is SA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 60 between Adrian Kuiper and Wessels

stories.title: A pathbreaking tour
stories.summary: India made her Test debut in 1932 and over the next sixty years played international matches against every Test playing nation except South Africa, for obvious reasons
